{
  "stem": "14091.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He fed me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He gave me to drink.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But apparently he thought that I will never survive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So he tried to keep me away from my sister, and he didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He kept me there for several days, or maybe more than a week, because I came to.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I start eating.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I start drinking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He cut off my hair with a scissors where you cut sheep.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And you could imagine how it looked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It was like in steps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But I never saw myself because I never saw a mirror.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I-- he felt, apparently, that I'm going to live, and he decided to tell my sister.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And our reunion-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I had also to tell her that I'm the only one.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Nobody escaped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[SIGHS] It was very-- it was so-- [SIGHS] I felt that it is more than a miracle that I myself survived this ordeal.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "By that time, Piotr let-- somehow he let know my brothers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "By that time, partisans were organized.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "My brothers, instead of being with the Jewish brigades that they tried to do themselves-- at that time, there were already many, many otriads that were organized, and my two brothers belonged to those.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Piotr let them know that not only [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Tzila ?] is with him, but also that I survived, and that I'm there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "One of the nights, they came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And this was, again, a repetition of our reunion and explaining what happened, and that I'm the only one survivor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They couldn't stay long because they belonged, at that time, in the partisans, and they were really like soldiers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "It was a regime.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And when they came, they took just one night leave of absence, and they only traveled in the night.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
